=CV 

= Education

- On February the 28th of 2025 I defended my Licentiate Thesis, which can be found in [\publications.html Publications]. 
Supervisor: [https://www.control.lth.se/personnel/personnel/anders-rantzer/ Anders Rantzer]. Opponent: [https://liu.se/en/employee/claal20 Claudio Altafini]. Examiner [https://portal.research.lu.se/en/persons/richard-pates/ Richard Pates].
- In July 2022 I received the Master's degree in [https://www.maths.lu.se/english/education/mathematics-masters-programme/ mathematics and numerical analysis] from [https://www.lunduniversity.lu.se Lund University]. 
Supervisor: [https://www.maths.lu.se/english/research/staff/claus-fuhrer/ Claus Führer]. Examiner: [https://portal.research.lu.se/en/persons/robert-kloefkorn/ Robert Klöfkorn] and [https://www.maths.lu.se/english/research/staff/philipp-birken/ Philipp Birken].
- In September 2020 I received the Bachelor's degree in [https://matematicas.ucm.es/estudios/grado-matematicas-plan mathematics] from [https://matematicas.ucm.es La Universidad Complutense de Madrid]. Supervisor: [https://www.ucm.es/mathqi/david-perez-garcia David Pérez García].

= Grants

- [https://www.fysiografen.se/en/ Royal Physiographic Society of Lund] Grant 2025. Endowment: Young researchers-PhD Students. Decision date: May 6, 2025. Amount: 25000 SEK.


